# PLC - Simple Encryption and Decryption Library

PLC is a lightweight Python library for performing simple encryption and decryption operations. It provides easy-to-use functions for converting text into binary strings for encryption and vice versa for decryption.

## Features

- Encrypt text into binary strings
- Decrypt binary strings back into text
- Simple and easy-to-use API

## Installation

You can install PLC using pip:

```bash
pip install PLC
